50x50, 100x100, and 200x200 input files for Blankenbach 1a (Ra=1.0e4, constant viscosity, 1x1 domain, steady state result)

To execute:

edit geoid.F and rheol.newt.F and comment out lines as needed

make clean

make picard (make sure that FFLAGS = -O2 -DIMPLICIT -DPICARD -I.)

conman.pic < run.bb2a50

